long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The extension supports getting Tiki360's information (customer id, order code, booking code, policy id, etc.), getting the name of the APIs for Tiki360's service, coping the curl command of the APIs for Tiki360's service, and auto-buying insurance.

The extension was developed by Tuan Nguyen, who is a software engineer.

The Tiki360's extension doesn't show ads and doesn't send users' data anywhere. It's fully open-source: https://github.com/nguyenvantuan2391996/tiki360-extension

Before you install it, disable similar extensions. Enjoy watching!
